item.title: Help with Project 16!
item.dc:creator: @hyper1 hyper1
item.description:
@hyper1 wrote:

Go into ur characters folder and click ur name look for character rights = 0. change the 0 to 3
3= owner. 2 = admin. 1 = player mod.
for the rest use the tutorial section and look for wat u need or use the search bar up at the tops of the page
hope that helped.
